### Chat Agent Bridge API

@access_token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJyb2xlcyI6WyJDVVNUT01FUiJdLCJ0b2tlblR5cGUiOiJBQ0NFU1MiLCJzdWIiOiJkZW1vLmN1c3RvbWVyQGVzaG9wLmxvY2FsIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgwMjQxNTE2LCJleHAiOjE3ODA2MDE1MTZ9.Jft_yOnlUrUEbKW2zMfyJqG1inmoDQhpMKMbaXzU_WA
@session_id = chat-session-001
@trace_id = chat-trace-001
@request_id = chat-request-001


### Send chat message through Spring bridge
### Requires CHAT_AGENT_ENABLED=true and CHAT_AGENT_BASE_URL pointing to the FastAPI chat-agent.

POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-trace-id: {{trace_id}}
x-request-id: {{request_id}}
traceparent: 00-4bf92f3577b34da6a3ce929d0e0e4736-00f067aa0ba902b7-00

{
  "message": "I need help finding a black jacket",
  "sessionId": "{{session_id}}",
  "traceId": "{{trace_id}}",
  "requestId": "{{request_id}}",
  "traceparent": "00-4bf92f3577b34da6a3ce929d0e0e4736-00f067aa0ba902b7-00",
  "pageContext": {
    "path": "/products",
    "locale": "en-US",
    "currency": "USD"
  }
}


### Disabled bridge check
### With default CHAT_AGENT_ENABLED=false this should return 503.

POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Will the bridge call FastAPI?",
  "sessionId": "{{session_id}}",
  "pageContext": {}
}


### Validation check: blank message should return 400

POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": " ",
  "sessionId": "{{session_id}}",
  "pageContext": {}
}
